<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?><map version="0.8.1"><node CREATED="1561600567067" ID="13k5dvusd1jgh6i2r9utki047u" MODIFIED="1561600567067" TEXT="09其他应用算法"><node CREATED="1561600567067" ID="1prg1pt4soos7nb24ba4g0mffl" MODIFIED="1561600567067" POSITION="right" TEXT="构建⼀个科学的排⾏榜体系"><node CREATED="1561600567067" ID="4rchbp5gp9kjetog4vc00blfvi" MODIFIED="1561600567067" TEXT="为什么要排⾏榜"><node CREATED="1561600567067" ID="3gbahkht8aem99sua4pmm7t7qc" MODIFIED="1561600567067" TEXT="⽤户冷启动问题"/><node CREATED="1561600567067" ID="3iclodu8u9ri863eiu3ko6ulfe" MODIFIED="1561600567067" TEXT="⽼⽤户的兴趣发现⽅式"/><node CREATED="1561600567067" ID="1a361n4s3ib4fr8pdjsrbkp9l4" MODIFIED="1561600567067" TEXT="降级的推荐系统"/></node><node CREATED="1561600567067" ID="5nv6jk18tl38kn8la7s6uv4bve" MODIFIED="1561600567067" TEXT="排⾏榜算法"><node CREATED="1561600567067" ID="6dh2qd3kg4qran2mef76hpihgu" MODIFIED="1561600567067" TEXT="按照销量去排序"><node CREATED="1561600567067" ID="00jsevindflnt54v2np810agnu" MODIFIED="1561600567067" TEXT="不靠谱"><node CREATED="1561600567067" ID="22in1s07h73cvbacgvodherhpi" MODIFIED="1561600567067" TEXT="1. ⾮常容易被攻击，也就是被刷榜；"/><node CREATED="1561600567067" ID="5a0ack5nn43dtplm76djljn8n5" MODIFIED="1561600567067" TEXT="2. ⻢太效应⼀直存在，除⾮强制替换，否则⼀些破了纪录的物品会⼀直占据在榜单中；"/><node CREATED="1561600567067" ID="3n2b8rc2l0scng28edr8uen14m" MODIFIED="1561600567067" TEXT="3. 不能反映出排⾏榜随着时间的变化，这⼀点和⻢太效应有关。"/></node></node><node CREATED="1561600567067" ID="2jmq73n9ed9kst0mt1a9tq244n" MODIFIED="1561600567067" TEXT="1.考虑时间因素"><node CREATED="1561600567067" ID="4cmh577fbj1r548m101vi8nsi9" MODIFIED="1561600567067" TEXT="Hacker News计算帖⼦的热度"><node CREATED="1561600567067" ID="3iej46bk6im088s9rdurrkmq7g" MODIFIED="1561600567067" TEXT="&lt;html&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;images/7465dm283ogmaup19go41muj0a.png&quot;&gt;"><node CREATED="1561600567070" ID="58uqjnjsucit0nnf7gdcaprp5f" MODIFIED="1561600567070" TEXT="1. P：得票数，去掉帖⼦作者⾃⼰投票。"/><node CREATED="1561600567070" ID="1g24h2ue3didbp8d0godrevffi" MODIFIED="1561600567070" TEXT="2. T：帖⼦距离现在的⼩时数，加上帖⼦发布到被转帖⾄Hacker News的平均时⻓"/><node CREATED="1561600567070" ID="7b6b71q0qfus248c2vtms1et7l" MODIFIED="1561600567070" TEXT="3. G：帖⼦热度的重⼒因⼦"/></node><node CREATED="1561600567070" ID="3s7qg4uojpku0cg5e7ruo8sn10" MODIFIED="1561600567070" TEXT="&lt;html&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;images/1jfltpig9lbvppoodhlq9bqulh.png&quot;&gt;"><node CREATED="1561600567073" ID="707siot5t4q5s2ma1n9871rujb" MODIFIED="1561600567073" TEXT="H：为环境温度，可以认为是平均票数，⽐如电商中的平均销量，由于不影响排序，可以不使⽤"/><node CREATED="1561600567074" ID="6nspcheff8vj1sh0r2ja4st9tp" MODIFIED="1561600567074" TEXT="C：为净剩票数，即时刻t物品已经得到的票数，也就是那个最朴素的统计量，⽐如商品的销量。"/><node CREATED="1561600567074" ID="255thbf519h74e7lmjgqpr30ls" MODIFIED="1561600567074" TEXT="t：为物品存在时间，⼀般以⼩时为单位。"/><node CREATED="1561600567074" ID="5po7tt9d4kmafuen3k1nj4mv88" MODIFIED="1561600567074" TEXT="$\alpha$ ：是冷却系数，反映物品⾃然冷却的快慢。"><node CREATED="1561600567074" ID="57e4d9umvvmhgiuq7odnu927vo" MODIFIED="1561600567074" TEXT="&lt;html&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;images/7jl63q3g7abruoloh8padr88ge.png&quot;&gt;"/></node></node></node></node><node CREATED="1561600567099" ID="6r73f5l04qeegvldbpo6m5f705" MODIFIED="1561600567099" TEXT="2.考虑三种投票"><node CREATED="1561600567099" ID="40kcm3emgpl8bok1ggcirsl1bc" MODIFIED="1561600567099" TEXT="1. 同样多的总票数，⽀持赞成票多的，因为这符合平台的⻓期利益；"/><node CREATED="1561600567099" ID="37vagprepa73f8ju8do4a03ect" MODIFIED="1561600567099" TEXT="2. 同样多的赞成票数，⽀持最有价值的，同样这符合平台⻓期利益。"/></node><node CREATED="1561600567099" ID="2uuhb1haekd8mdtltavl3a488o" MODIFIED="1561600567099" TEXT="3.考虑好评的平均程度"><node CREATED="1561600567099" ID="6eupgb53v62mb9v886afbqn2ag" MODIFIED="1561600567099" TEXT="⻉叶斯平均"><node CREATED="1561600567099" ID="4sgl42amao91o776bm45l1dgmc" MODIFIED="1561600567099" TEXT="&lt;html&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;images/444nvs9kj5kbr4gamvtk6dr4da.png&quot;&gt;"><node CREATED="1561600567101" ID="6o6020slpkke52drdlnbse7r9v" MODIFIED="1561600567101" TEXT="R，物品的平均得分，这个很简单，有多少⼈评分，把他们评分加起来除以⼈数就是了；"/><node CREATED="1561600567102" ID="3pt6tc90r2dqsliq8uts5um1rf" MODIFIED="1561600567102" TEXT="v，参与为这个物品评分的⼈数；"/><node CREATED="1561600567102" ID="618mnif82f45qi0do5b3u98vun" MODIFIED="1561600567102" TEXT="m，全局平均每个物品的评分⼈数；"/><node CREATED="1561600567102" ID="2b5oh9to0qa7lhjemu3oum9v2c" MODIFIED="1561600567102" TEXT="C，全局平均每个物品的平均得分；"/></node></node></node></node></node><node CREATED="1561600567102" ID="4vmdpqsleblk3sovp8od9ouioh" MODIFIED="1561600567102" POSITION="right" TEXT="实⽤的加权采样算法"><node CREATED="1561600567102" ID="1fn4rj2bboofb2jkrmmv7stleq" MODIFIED="1561600567102" TEXT="好处"><node CREATED="1561600567102" ID="6vps9o5nvaea8ah13sr2duprpp" MODIFIED="1561600567102" TEXT="1. ⼤⼤减少召回时的计算复杂度；"/><node CREATED="1561600567102" ID="67mh0vr85g2kdr5404babn9l76" MODIFIED="1561600567102" TEXT="2. 可以保留更多的⽤户标签；"/><node CREATED="1561600567102" ID="1nf3qae72f9k7jui3l7lhlkbtt" MODIFIED="1561600567102" TEXT="3. 每次召回计算时还能有所变化；"/><node CREATED="1561600567102" ID="7ri0t7iokg8icbvnua2hvagnaf" MODIFIED="1561600567102" TEXT="4. 虽然有变化，但是依然受标签的权重相对⼤⼩约束"/></node><node CREATED="1561600567102" ID="6vbvbg27oq4k6jr23hfe7oo45j" MODIFIED="1561600567102" TEXT="加权采样"><node CREATED="1561600567102" ID="3lssp403m4ubms4ti5381la964" MODIFIED="1561600567102" TEXT="1.有限数据集"><node CREATED="1561600567102" ID="14e1dhqdnja3pgq7mboirdkp7l" MODIFIED="1561600567102" TEXT="&lt;html&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;images/0lngj5lbj147dvevc1lvbj6sdu.png&quot;&gt;"><node CREATED="1561600567104" ID="4p01d6hhjhsuse2bglut349495" MODIFIED="1561600567104" TEXT="1. wi 是每个样本的权重，⽐如⽤户标签权重；"/><node CREATED="1561600567104" ID="1hli2r24uvhskhajfkr2tomk1d" MODIFIED="1561600567104" TEXT="2. R是遍历每个样本时产⽣的0到1之间的随机数；"/><node CREATED="1561600567104" ID="1ln9203von5puk9estetaajsi0" MODIFIED="1561600567104" TEXT="3. Si就是每个样本的采样分数"/></node></node><node CREATED="1561600567104" ID="174lkdiub97d5d79p1mhlpg62t" MODIFIED="1561600567104" TEXT="2.⽆限数据集"><node CREATED="1561600567104" ID="7mooac4knlu6ct94k21lqgj2qm" MODIFIED="1561600567104" TEXT="1. 为每⼀个样本⽣成⼀个分数，分数还是⽤这个公式 $S_{i} = R^{\frac{1}{w_{i}}}$;"/><node CREATED="1561600567104" ID="28vcsru1ciiissm1q8t5338mdb" MODIFIED="1561600567104" TEXT="2. 如果结果不⾜k个，直接保存到结果中"/><node CREATED="1561600567104" ID="66km2n13lee6ofmasc21euvb2m" MODIFIED="1561600567104" TEXT="3. 如果结果中已经有k个了，如果 $S_{i}$ ⽐已有的结果⾥最⼩那个分数⼤，就替换它"/></node></node></node><node CREATED="1561600567104" ID="3fe91qg0qhk5t6ufkrolqn3fbk" MODIFIED="1561600567104" POSITION="left" TEXT="推荐候选池的去重策略"><node CREATED="1561600567104" ID="2v5utcnlj7ktsueu3epjrp5i8k" MODIFIED="1561600567104" TEXT="Simhash"/><node CREATED="1561600567104" ID="0er255ar9964prsu3dmnn1llsm" MODIFIED="1561600567104" TEXT="Bloomfilter"/></node></node></map>